Package: landconn
Type: Package
Title: Landscape Connectivity
Version: 0.5.0
Authors@R:
    person("Bill", "Peterman", email = "peterman.73@osu.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Calculates landscape connectivity metrics and provides tools to
    assess connectivity across resistance surfaces. Includes incidence function
    connectivity and wrappers that run 'Circuitscape' from R through
    'JuliaConnectoR'. Developed for teaching and research.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
  R (>= 4.3)
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
URL: https://github.com/wpeterman/landconn
